data.description:
*$10,000 credit towards rate buy down/closing costs* This stunning J Hill home is located in a highly desirable neighborhood, offering a combination of elegance, functionality, and modern design. Don't let the room count fool you. This home features an additional room that could easily be used as a 4th bedroom, in addition to the office that is right by the primary.  As you approach the home, you are greeted by its charming curb appeal. Featuring meticulous landscaping, architectural design which showcases a harmonious blend of classic and contemporary elements, creating a timeless aesthetic. Upon entering, you are immediately struck by an open floor plan with a spacious living room bathed in natural light, thanks to large windows that offer picturesque views of the back patio, large yard and outdoor fireplace. 
The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream. It features custom cabinetry, a hidden coffee bar, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a center island, perfect for both casual family meals and formal dinner parties.
The primary suite is a private oasis within the home. It offers a generous bedroom with plush carpeting, a walk-in closet with built-in organizers, and an en-suite bathroom. The primary is attached to the laundry room. 
The two additional bedrooms are spacious and well-appointed sharing a Jack and Jill bathroom. 
The garage provides plenty of space for parking vehicles, storage, or a workshop area. The neighborhood is meticulously designed, with tree-lined streets, well-maintained sidewalks, and beautifully landscaped common areas. The community offers a sense of tranquility making it an ideal place to raise a family or enjoy a peaceful retirement. The local school district is renowned for its academic excellence. Families can take comfort in knowing that their children will receive a top-notch education. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this dream home in an amazing neighborhood. Buyers/buyers agent to verify all information.
